ne connection made by the caller.::FR_the words 24-Hour Number or Numro 24 heures, or an abbreviation of these words, followed by a telephone number, including the area code, at which the consignor can be reached immediately for technical information about the dangerous goods in transport, without breaking the telephone connection made by the caller.')
